<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA62">
<l>puṇarmaruti ṉūṭupōyp pūṅkuruntañ cāyttu</l>
<l>maṇamaruva mālviṭai yēḻceṟṟuk – kaṇamveruva</l>
<l>vēḻulakun tāyiṉavu meṇṭicaiyum pōyiṉavuñ</l>
<l>cūḻaravap poṅkaṇaiyāṉ ṟōḷ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>After going between the joined myrobalan trees, bending down the flowering wild lime tree</l>
<l>[and] subduing the seven huge bulls in order to unite in marriage,</l>
<l>they leapt over the seven worlds so that the hosts [of Asuras] were frightened</l>
<l>and went into all eight directions, the arms of him on the undulating bed</l>
<l>of the serpent that envelops [him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
